title: 15 Chess Books - March 2016 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 15 chess books in PDF format:

01. A Complete Guide to the Grivas Sicilian by Efstratios Grivas
02. Caro-Kann Smyslov System 4...Nd7 by Eduard Gufeld, Oleg Stetsko
03. Chess Strategy for the Tournament Player Lev Alburt, Semyon Palatnik
04. Chess Tips for the Improving Player by Amatzia Avni
05. Dvoretsky's Endgame Manual (2nd Ed) by Mark Dvoretsky
06. Leonid Stein - Master of Risk and Strategy by Eduard Gufeld, Efim Lazarev
07. Secrets of Pawn Endings b y Jarsten Muller, Frank Lamprecht
08. Selected Chess Games of Mikhail Tal by J. Hajtun
09. Shall We Play Fischerandom Chess? by Svetozar Gligoric
10. Sicilian Kalashnikov by Jan Pinski, Jacob Aagaard
11. Squeezing the Gambits by Kiril Georgiev
12. Teach Yourself Chess (4th Ed) by William Hartston
13. The Quickest Chess Victories of All Time by Graham Burgess
14. Winning at Correspondence Chess by Tim Harding
15. Winning Pawn Structures by Alexander Baburin
